<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.2.1">
<l>kācai yāṭai mūṭiyōṭik kātalcey tāṉavaṉūr</l>
<l>nāca māka nampavalla nampi namperumāṉ</l>
<l>vēyi ṉaṉṉa tōḷmaṭavār veṇṇeyuṇ ṭāṉivaṉeṉ</l>
<l>ṟēca niṉṟa vemperumā ṉevvuḷ kiṭantāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our great lord, the mighty noble who desired the ruin</l>
<l rend="indent">of the city of the Dānava</l>
<l>Who, covered in russet clothes, hastily acted [with] lust,</l>
<l>Our lord who endured when the simple ladies with bamboo-like arms scolded,</l>
<l>Saying, “This is the one who ate the butter,” he is the one who lies in Evvuḷ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
